name: Corrsk  (Genarius)
content: Corrsk was a Trandoshan who lived on the planet Genarius during the waning years of the Galactic Republic. Corrsk and fellow Trandoshan Dussk owned and operated the cantina Riboga's Barge, a sail barge that was formerly owned by the Hutt Riboga. The pair were openly disdainful of Riboga and Hutts in general, and when Riboga returned to the Cularin system during the time of the Clone Wars, he sent the assassin Kills to murder Corrsk and Dussk, to make an example of them.
